# Changelog - EPICS Major Mode for Emacs
## [unreleased]
### Changed
- Change CL "equalp" predicate with elisp "equal"

## [0.4.2] - 2020.09.10
### Added
- Functions for following links

## [0.4.1] - 2020.08.16
### Added
- Customisation group, only for setting number of indentation spaces
### Fixed
- Indentation function should not do anything if already at desired indent (to preserve undo history)

## [0.4.0] - 2020.08.14
### Added
- Basic indentation calculation functions
### Changed
- Dehardcoded keywords

## [0.3.1] - 2020.03.20
### Changed
- Improve asyn regex to allow multiple macros
- Separate asyn and streamdevice regexes

## [0.3.0] - 2020.03.16
### Added
- Finish adding epics keywords for menuChoices, stream and asyn dtypes

### Changed
- menu-choices are now refered to as keywords

## [0.2.2] - 2020.03.12
### Added
- Autoload for .db, .dbd, .template files
- LICENCE file
- MSS to epics-link-params

## Changed
- Reverse regex order, so syntax colors correctly
- Change mode name to 'EPICS'

## [0.2.1] - 2020.03.09
### Fixed
- MenuChoices syntax coloring should not color quotation marks

## [0.2.0] - 2020.03.09
### Changed
- MenuChoices are now highlighted

## [0.1.1] - 2020.03.05
### Added
- Highlighting for CA, CPP, CP, NPP, PP, NMS and MS
- comment-dwim functionality
- README.md

## [0.1.0] - 2020.03.01
### Added
- Different highlighting of records if they are input, output or general
- Highlighting of input and output fields, some fields related to scanning, alarm fields
- Comment, macro and string highlighting
